Title: [ANN][PRE-TGE] A GREEN REVOLUTION IN THE INDUSTRY OF LUBRICANTS | Valena-SVC
Body: Valena-SV complexes ensure protection against hydrogen wear, which results in smaller amount of dust in oil, and consequently filter gets longer-lasting. Due to applying metal plaque technology friction becomes sliding friction, so contact area of rubbing surfaces is reduced by 5 times. Copper ion membrane preserves its self-healing properties throughout oil lifespan. Copper ion membrane allows to reduce lubricants temperature by 20-30 degrees Celsius (we can show copper membrane).  Unlike our competitors counterpart Valena-SV is much better at keeping engine clean from sludge and securing sludge suspended in the oil. When its used the second time and more engine remains clean forever whereas amount of Valena-SV additive may be decreased and thus less money is spent on oil. We dont play planned wearout game which many car and oil producers participate in. Thats why we are free to make lubricants up to the standard of unique Russian military technologies for the global market.

Author: Mang86
Title: [ANN][PRE-TGE] A GREEN REVOLUTION IN THE INDUSTRY OF LUBRICANTS | Valena-SVC
Body: Valena-SV complexes ensure protection against hydrogen wear, which results in smaller amount of dust in oil, and consequently filter gets longer-lasting. Due to applying metal plaque technology friction becomes sliding friction, so contact area of rubbing surfaces is reduced by 5 times. Copper ion membrane preserves its self-healing properties throughout oil lifespan. Copper ion membrane allows to reduce lubricants temperature by 20-30 degrees Celsius (we can show copper membrane).  Unlike our competitors counterpart Valena-SV is much better at keeping engine clean from sludge and securing sludge suspended in the oil. When its used the second time and more engine remains clean forever whereas amount of Valena-SV additive may be decreased and thus less money is spent on oil. We dont play planned wearout game which many car and oil producers participate in. Thats why we are free to make lubricants up to the standard of unique Russian military technologies for the global market.

Author: Mang86
Title: [ANN][PRE-TGE] A GREEN REVOLUTION IN THE INDUSTRY OF LUBRICANTS | Valena-SVC
Body: Oil plays a huge role in the engine! Let's talk a little about what happens when you add our product to the engine. The Valena-SV engine additive forms a 1-2 micron protective ion film on the friction surfaces. Thanks to the ion film, the internal mobile units begin to work in the mode of non-wear friction. Ion film protects engine parts from hydrogen wear, preventing the formation of metallic dust (chips) in the oil. As a result, the life of filters and parts increases. Ion film thickness of about two microns covers the microcracks, which leads to a noticeable reduction in noise and vibration. Copper ions actively take away heat from the foci of friction, slowing the burning and oxidation of the oil. The temperature of the oil in the friction nodes is reduced by 20-30 degrees, increasing the service life of the oil by 2-3 times. All this leads to a reduction in emissions and fuel economy.

Author: Mang86
Title: [ANN][PRE-TGE] A GREEN REVOLUTION IN THE INDUSTRY OF LUBRICANTS | Valena-SVC
Body: No problem, dear friend. Using our additive, you reduce the load on your engine and optimize its performance. This is something like vitamins for the engine. Taking such "vitamins" the engine starts to work better and release less harmful substances into the environment, and also longer serve you.

Author: Mang86
Title: [ANN][PRE-TGE] A GREEN REVOLUTION IN THE INDUSTRY OF LUBRICANTS | Valena-SVC
Body: When adding our additive to the engine, it starts consuming less gasoline, and the service life is increased by two to three times. That is, you can spend less money on fuel and the replacement of oil, which in turn will bring you a profit. Read more about the technology itself in our white paper.

Author: Mang86
Title: [ANN][PRE-TGE] A GREEN REVOLUTION IN THE INDUSTRY OF LUBRICANTS | Valena-SVC
Body: Of course I understand. There is nothing to be afraid of, let's take such a competitor as the Oronite Company. This is our biggest indirect competitor. Unlike Oronite additives Valena-SV complexes ensure protection against hydrogen wear, which results in smaller amount of dust in oil, and consequently filter gets longer-lasting. Due to applying metal plaque technology friction becomes sliding friction, so contact area of rubbing surfaces is reduced by 5 times. Copper ion membrane preserves its self-healing properties throughout oil lifespan. Copper ion membrane allows to reduce lubricants temperature by 20-30 degrees Celsius (we can show copper membrane).  Unlike our competitors counterpart Valena-SV is much better at keeping engine clean from sludge and securing sludge suspended in the oil. When its used the second time and more engine remains clean forever whereas amount of Valena-SV additive may be decreased and thus less money is spent on oil. We dont play planned wearout game which many car and oil producers participate in. Thats why we are free to make lubricants up to the standard of unique Russian military technologies for the global market.

Title: [ANN][PRE-TGE] A GREEN REVOLUTION IN THE INDUSTRY OF LUBRICANTS | Valena-SVC
Body: Great question! Oils must move to a new level. The state of the world's ecology requires that. Developments by Professor Garkunov reduce friction by 60 times, prevent the wear of parts, stop the burning of oils, reduce harmful emissions into the atmosphere, save fuel or electricity. The whole world should apply these technologies, which were crowdsale in the Soviet Union and have now continued to develop.   Now when maximizing profits is the main the idea of programmed wearout has won. There is aconspiracy  between oil producers of oils and machinery mkers. This cant keep on going like this! Our planet wont withstand such reckless overuse of natural resources!   Our Valena-SV additives can change the overall  picture and approach to the use of oils. We will try to make our contribution by means of  blockchain technology. The oil must be changed when its required. Timely chemical tests of the oil will be run, which will allow to monitor the condition of the oil and give recommendations when it is really necessary to change the oil, in case there is wear of the parts or  soot accumulates itself. The oil condition indicators  show the problems in the equipment operation, this may help to  prevent a breakdown. Blockchain will allow to accumulate information on the use of oils and distribute statistical information among in the blockchain network around the world, give advice to users about the use of lubricants and additives around the world. Counterfeits goods are a big problem on the lubricant market. Blockchain will enble us to eliminate faking of our products.   Thanks for the interesting question!

Author: Mang86
Title: [ANN][PRE-TGE] A GREEN REVOLUTION IN THE INDUSTRY OF LUBRICANTS | Valena-SVC
Body: Hello dear friend! Unlike Oronite additives Valena-SV complexes ensure protection against hydrogen wear, which results in smaller amount of dust in oil, and consequently filter gets longer-lasting. Due to applying metal plaque technology friction becomes sliding friction, so contact area of rubbing surfaces is reduced by 5 times. Copper ion membrane preserves its self-healing properties throughout oil lifespan. Copper ion membrane allows to reduce lubricants temperature by 20-30 degrees Celsius (we can show copper membrane).  Unlike our competitors counterpart Valena-SV is much better at keeping engine clean from sludge and securing sludge suspended in the oil. When its used the second time and more engine remains clean forever whereas amount of Valena-SV additive may be decreased and thus less money is spent on oil. We dont play planned wearout game which many car and oil producers participate in. Thats why we are free to make lubricants up to the standard of unique Russian military technologies for the global market.

We advocate for decentralization that is why our dealers and partners will have their own blockchain hubs. We dont want our network to be centralized. As we have more than one thousand partners the network will be highly decentralized.

Author: Mang86
Title: [ANN][PRE-TGE] A GREEN REVOLUTION IN THE INDUSTRY OF LUBRICANTS | Valena-SVC
Body: Hi dear friend! Very interesting question! Indeed basics for these complexes were developed at the end of last century in the USSR and all foremost scientific and industrial achievements of that time in the defense industry were applied in the complexes. The resources the USSR contributed in R&D of lubricants are not available to any multinational organization. The developments are still in active use by Russian military air force. In 1990 Valena was successfully introduced to the major car-producing enterprise ZIL in Moscow. However, in 1991 after the USSR collapse these developments fell into disuse. And only due to enthusiasm of young Russian scientists and businessmen this technology has come into use for peaceful purposes. Now 30 years after it was developed Valena-SV has almost no counterpart in the world.
